{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-95","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sophie deli svoj uobičajeni raspored za subotu, uključujući vreme kada se budi i određene aktivnosti. Pogledajte pravilnu upotrebu veznika i vremenskih fraza.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-95"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koja je tačna informacija/rečenica o rasporedu Sofije za subotu?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She wakes up at 9:00, cleans her house, and watches a movie.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Sofija spominje da spava <span class=\"highlighted-text\">until 9:30</span>, nije <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wakes up at 9:00</span>.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She sleeps until 10:00 and does house cleaning in the morning.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Sophie kaže da spava <span class=\"highlighted-text\">until 9:30</span>, je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">10:00</span>.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She gets up at 9:30, does some housework, watches a movie at home or goes to the mall.</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She wakes up early, goes jogging, and spends the afternoon reading at home.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Raspored Sofije ne uključuje trčanje ili učenje.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company1-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Sophie","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"